data.description: Welcome to a rare opportunity to own a versatile multi-unit property in the highly sought-after Normal Heights neighborhood. The front home is a 2 bedroom/2 bath that is bathed in natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere that extends throughout each room. The back studio is completely detached and perfect for providing the flexibility of multi-generational living or income-producing potential. Both homes have their own, outdoor spaces adorned with drought-tolerant plants, offering a serene and low-maintenance setting for relaxation and entertaining. This property has been thoughtfully upgraded, seamlessly blending modern enhancements with the original charm of the home. Whether you're looking to accommodate multi-generational living or seeking an income-generating asset, this property offers endless possibilities. Don't miss out on this opportunity as they are rare and in high demand.
